{"tid":1287993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐懼往往是政府的終極武器","createTime":"2019-07-05T12:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T18:08:27.000Z","uid":181257,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"75bb7ccc60ab3c8683a03e41054eb705bf4b5ff8","tid":1287993,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"唔好以後搞白色恐怖我哋就驚，香港人經過今次，腦容量已經大增，唔再係金魚記憶。我哋永遠都會記得有四位捐軀嘅朋友，唔好放棄 爭取到底！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）"},{"pid":"128939845661e1dc7db734a5349a4d3ad4bf617b","tid":1287993,"uid":267801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"AI 人工智能示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894120547a8b84c7a0568d3296492d9a67e55a97","tid":1287993,"uid":37055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得套戲 每一句都鼓勵到我"},{"pid":"bbcaec5311d0d163e31be8882edd92dd521ba041","tid":1287993,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128939845661e1dc7db734a5349a4d3ad4bf617b","tid":1287993,"uid":267801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"AI 人工智能示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"detroit"},{"pid":"34e9bed86ae80bdddae9144882ea7a228a4b7a2d","tid":1287993,"uid":181257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。<br />\n<br />\n我哋帶嘅每一具口罩，都藏著一個理念<br />\n唔會受強權打壓 <br />\n唔係被暴力威脅<br />\n唔會因時間消失"},{"pid":"4a659d1422d303a84552a3f05a5cb6ed7ffccd0d","tid":1287993,"uid":18948,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-aqx8-EO9CrU/VJg_DFWtcEI/AAAAAAAAAFs/2PePy9x7ydY/s1600/hope.gif\" data-thumbna